    <note>Li(2) Yingji [1120] His granddaughter's father-in-law was Guo(1) Quan [942]. Yingji was Guo(1) Maoxun's [953] maternal great grandfather. His great great granddaughter, who died in 1089 at the age of 21, was married to an imperial clansman, Zhao(1) Shizhu(2) [17774]. See also documentation for son-in-law, Zhao(1) Kexie [17769] (q.v.). Fan Zuyu, WJ, 47.14b; XCB, 76.4a, 78.10b; Guangdong TZ, 14.21a; SHY:SH, 49.12a. CBD, 2, 1058.</note>
